        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[2024 Swift 学生挑战赛开启报名，50 名杰出获奖者将获邀参观苹果总部]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-vmark="5da7"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 2 月 6 日消息，苹果今日宣布开启 2024 Swift 学生挑战赛的报名通道。作为一项鼓励学生开发者创新的全球性赛事，苹果表示：「我们很荣幸能通过 Swift 学生挑战赛支持和培养下一代开发人员、创意工作者和企业家。」</p><p style="text-align: center;" data-vmark="d29b"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/2/b16b3840-d292-4321-8d59-e35ab5a5e3be.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1500" h="750" data-advance="W3siVHlwZSI6IndlYnAiLCJVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL2ltZy5pdGhvbWUuY29tL25ld3N1cGxvYWRmaWxlcy8yMDI0LzIvN2M1MmRjMTQtMjVkZC00YTdkLTkyMWUtNzM3NmQ4MGM3MDZlLndlYnAifV0=" title="2024 Swift 学生挑战赛开启报名，50 名杰出获奖者将获邀参观苹果总部" width="1500" height="410" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c0dd">据 IT 之家了解，挑战赛鼓励学生利用 App Playgrounds 开发应用程序，展示他们的创意和编程能力。这些作品不仅可以解决实际问题，更能帮助学生获得未来职业所需的技能。</p><p data-vmark="d510">对 Swift 学生挑战赛感兴趣的学生可以登录<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717546478312&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2F%3Fcid%3Dapple-newsroom&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=Apple%E2%80%99s%20developer%20website" target="_blank">苹果开发者网站</a>注册报名，报名通道将在未来三周内开放。最终将选出 350 名获奖者，其中 50 名表现出色的「杰出获奖者」将获邀于明年夏天前往苹果总部园区参观交流。所有获奖者都将获得一年期的苹果开发者计划会员资格、一份免费参加 Swift 应用开发认证考试的优惠券以及一份来自苹果的特别礼物。</p><blockquote><p data-vmark="6643">今年的挑战赛新增了「杰出获奖者」类别，将在 350 名获奖者中选出 50 位表现最为出色的学生，并邀请他们前往库比蒂诺的苹果总部参加独家体验活动。所有获奖者都将获得一年期的苹果开发者计划会员资格、一份免费参加 Swift 应用开发认证考试的优惠券以及一份来自苹果的特别礼物。</p></blockquote><p data-vmark="03db">有关<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717549691816&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2Feligibility%2F&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=on%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20website" target="_blank">参赛资格要求</a>和<a href="https://redirect.viglink.com/?format=go&amp;jsonp=vglnk_170717550667118&amp;key=c1c7d488bb2df8a8b659d5d41634d304&amp;libId=ls9jxvwn010023dg000UL1ohhofmz14652&amp;loc=https%3A%2F%2F9to5mac.com%2F2024%2F02%2F05%2F2024-swift-student-challenge%2F&amp;gppConsent=DBABBg~BUoAAAA&amp;ccpaConsent=1YNN&amp;v=1&amp;out=https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.apple.com%2Fswift-student-challenge%2Fget-ready%2F&amp;title=Apple%20opens%202024%20Swift%20Student%20Challenge%20applications%20with%20new%20%27Distinguished%20Winners%27%20category%20-%209to5Mac&amp;txt=learning%20resources%20for%20students" target="_blank">学习资源</a>的详细信息，请访问苹果开发者网站。</p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
        ]]>
